    "46305": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Kaeya",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Izzard",
                    "T": "How embarrassing... Having my life saved by a knight..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Don't forget what you promised... or that thing will be the least of your worries."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Izzard",
                    "T": "Hey... Is this how the Knights of Favonius treats the people they catch?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "I'm just joking. Alright... Let's take him back."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Knight of Favonius",
                    "T": "Sir! Yes sir!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Knight of Favonius",
                    "T": "Captain, should we take these two in as well?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Haha, of course not. They are the ones who made this arrest possible."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Without them spreading our <color=#00E1FFFF>fabricated intel</color>, we wouldn't have been able to catch the Treasure Hoarders."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "So the intel is fake."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "There is no treasure."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You lied to us?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "*cries* You're a bad man for lying to me... Shame on the Knights!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Alright, alright... Stop it already."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Though the treasure doesn't exist, you did want it for yourself, didn't you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Otherwise, you would have informed me of your intentions, no?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That... well... ah... Hmph!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Let's go, {NICKNAME}. Paimon's done talking to him!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Ha. Just a sec."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "You did help me out, so you do deserve a reward."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "This is the \"Triumphant Harbinger of Dawn That Points Towards Victory.\" As its name suggests, it symbolizes light and victory."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "If you don't mind, I would like to present you with this Harbinger of Dawn as a reward."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Harbinger of Dawn?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "That's right. It suits a well-cultured and disciplined person such as yourself, wouldn't you say, Paimon?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well... If the reward is this Harbinger of Dawn..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "You'd forgive me, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "I'm honored to have such an understanding friend."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yes... yes..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "You have my apologies for the deception. I will not use the same method twice."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "...Paimon has been completely charmed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Means you'll use a different method next time?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "What a wonderful day. Now, I have to go interrogate my suspect..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
